1. Information We Collect

This bot may collect certain information to provide its functionality, including:

    User IDs and server IDs to identify and interact with users
    Message content (only if necessary to fulfill a bot function, otherwise no messages are stored)
    Any other data explicitly submitted by the user to the bot

2. How We Use Your Information

The information collected by the bot is used solely to enable its functionality and improve the user experience. We do not sell or share user data with third parties.

3. Data Storage and Security

We take appropriate security measures to protect the data collected by the bot. User data is stored securely and retained only for as long as necessary for the botâ€™s functionality.

4. User Rights

You have the right to:

    Request access to any data the bot has stored about you
    Request deletion of your data where applicable

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted here, and users are encouraged to review the policy periodically.

6. Contact

For any questions or concerns about these policies, please contact us at support@mafe-systems.org
